Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:03.24,Sign Center,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}5th Grade, Class 4\NKayo Hinazuki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been\Nfor the last few days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the ones behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing,\Nhiding someone else's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You made me worried about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared because I'm going to sue!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you looked for Kayo at all\Nduring the past three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... trying to paint me\Nas the bad guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:00:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! Let go of me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Made you worried about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were only worried about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:37.23,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you doing, Kayo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! You're not gonna listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Ms. Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo doesn't want to see you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?! Treating me\Nlike a bad guy in front of Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are,\Nkidnapping someone else's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of parent throws\Nher daughter in a shed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and doesn't do anything\Nafter she's gone for three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea about the pains\Nand responsibilities of being a parent, brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you shut your smart mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are Ms. Akemi Hinazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're with the Ishikari Development\NBureau's Child Consultation Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to discuss\Nyour daughter Kayo with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed you wouldn't agree\Nto meet with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so we enlisted\NMs. Fujinuma's cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who ever said I wouldn't meet you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my presumptuousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I asked you to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, Mr. Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a few words for her too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm actually grateful\Nthat I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're the criminals\Nfor abducting my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Call the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, first we need to discuss your\Nusual relationship with your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about my relationship with Kayo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've decided that your daughter, Kayo,\Nneeds to be taken into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Into custody?! I'm her guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You revoked your guardianship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by failing to look for your daughter\Nwhen she went missing for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of that brat over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you treating me\Nlike a criminal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right, Ms. Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the police myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They can settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- W-Wait, Ms. Hinazuki!\N- We need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've been estranged ever since\NI made you break up with that man,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I've been worried about you\Nand Kayo all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know very well how hard it is\Nfor a woman to raise a child on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should have helped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I made you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.88,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DIVORCE REGISTRATION
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,take all of it on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't think badly of Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet those tears were out of self-pity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kayo wasn't moved either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wouldn't look\Nat her weeping mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi, don't worry about Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:07:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My child is the most precious thing\NI have in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must have thought\Nthe same way at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the one\Nwho got me in gear, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your heroic efforts just\Ncouldn't end in tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's going to be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hardly have any memory of my father,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I wonder if he talked like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for getting me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Town Without Me,"\Nby Kayo Hinazuki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I get bigger, big enough\Nto go somewhere by myself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to go to a land that's far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to go to a faraway island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to go to an island\Nthat has no people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to go to an island\Nthat has no pain or sadness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.57,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for dinner!\NNext time, I want to cook with you.\N-Kayo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On that island, I can climb\Na tree when I want to climb,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}swim in the sea when I want to swim,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sleep when I want to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I think about the town\Nwithout me, I feel a sense of relief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to go far, far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saved Kayo at last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fastened her life to the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From now on,\NKayo will make her own mark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have faith that the future\NKayo faces is a bright place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Episode 9\NClosure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru's been like this all day.\NDo you think he's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hero for helping Hinazuki, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Satoru, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look fine at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't blame him.\NI mean, with Hinazuki gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Although that does bring closure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:52.66,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STAFF ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About Kayo's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll be able to see\NKayo for a number of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's going to begin a new life\Nwith her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you said, "Your heroic efforts\Njust couldn't end in tragedy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, it may have\Nsounded a little vulgar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if I'd said "the reward\Nfor your heroic efforts,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but what you did was deserving\Nof a reward, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want?\NTo see Kayo smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Satoru,\Nwas Kayo in your house all that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. We had a hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- A hideout?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We hid Kayo in the bus Izumi Elementary's\Nhockey club used to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A place that only kidnappers\Nlike you guys would think to go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't really laugh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.36,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kayo's gone now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.78,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYA NAKANISHI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the killer is still targeting\NHiromi and Aya Nakanishi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.57,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIROMI SUGITA\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:10.12,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIROMI SUGITA\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:10.12,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYA NAKANISHI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:10.12,Sign Right,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to make sure neither one\Nof them are left alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like with Kayo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.25,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT, WONDER GUY!\NTV THEME SONG
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiromi is my classmate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Aya Nakanishi goes\Nto Izumi Elementary next door,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so it'll be hard to approach her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear she's often with Yuuki, but\Nhow can I start a conversation with her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She doesn't know anything about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a pretty high hurdle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A way to become friends\Nwith someone you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just be straightforward,\Nlike, "Let's be friends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like that would—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking,\N"Like that would work," aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she read my mind?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've already got Kayo, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to trick you\Ninto fessing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she's always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be so pessimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should focus on a positive result.\NNothing ventured, nothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.18,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have stop somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya and Hiromi,\Nyou're going to the center, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll meet you there later. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.69,Place,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WITH YUUKI BY THE RIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.16,Place,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HAMANASU PRIVATE CRAM SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:41.67,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HAMANASU PRIVATE CRAM SCHOOL\NGRADE COURSES
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she gets out of cram school at 6:30.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be able to walk Hiromi home\Nand get back here in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First I have to investigate\Nher basic activity pattern.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.46,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WITH HIROMI AND KENYA\NAT THE CHILDREN'S RECREATION CENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.76,Sign Right Large,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEAVING HIROMI AND KENYA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.14,Place,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CRAM SCHOOL LETS OUT\NBEGIN TAILING AYA NAKANISHI AGAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aya Nakanishi's daily activity\Nschedule was simple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she were going to be abducted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it would most likely happen\Nin this time slot, after cram school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to make sure she got home,\Nso don't suddenly appear like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you buy all this in one trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was cheap, so I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain!\NThat only makes it heavier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy even if I don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom binged on groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say I binged!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you married?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have\Na partner to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then it depends on your\Npartner's feelings, mutual timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, various things... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been through a painful\Nexperience once,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe I'm proceeding\Nwith excessive caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.\NIt's not a bad question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was going to ask you\Nsomething else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How to approach a girl you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know about her,\Nbut she doesn't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the cautious type, so even if it'd be\Nbeating around the bush,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd start by getting her\Nto relax her guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Relax her guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Put another way, charm her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're good at sports or cooking,\Nwhatever, use it as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When she becomes\Ninterested in whatever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she lets her guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at expressing my\Nfeelings directly, so I just rely on logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something's sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorr—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Candy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've seen,\Nthere's no sense in hiding it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have some too,\Nso you become equally guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I quit smoking three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,candy has been my go-to substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In private, I can't relax without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-He's weird...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to the center\Nto do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hiromi! I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First Hinazuki, and now it's like\Nyou're Hiromi's guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, can I speak to you in private?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hiromi. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, honestly,\Nwhat are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your determination\Nto save Hinazuki, and that went well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but looking at you, I still get the sense\Nthat something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, if something's up,\Nwill you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really explain it.\NIt's too much of a leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make that leap, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be a superhero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a "part two,"\Ntake me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenya, what do you think\Nof these footprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An adult's, coming and going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you look carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The shoes were wrapped in cloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not to keep from slipping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe to keep from leaving\Nshoe sole imprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The backpack is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the box with the briquette\Nisn't here anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think there are fewer\Nboxes here overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And a lot of them are torn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must have made off\Nwith their contents only.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Kayo was staying here alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do you remember about the man\Nwho came here in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who gave off a dangerous vibe\Nbased on the stuff he left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's a killer\Nwho targets children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru? I don't know\Nwhere you're getting this from...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's unbelievable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when I saw the contents\Nof the backpack and the briquette,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it made me think this was where a serial\Nkiller kept his murderous tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it all sounds insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you now, with Kayo too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to leave her alone\Njust to keep her mother from abusing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but also to protect her from this killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, do you mean to become\Na novelist or detective in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the issue is whether\Nwhat you're saying is far-fetched or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's whether I believe or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:43.28,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine without you walking me\Nall this way. I am a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I have business\Nin the neighborhood anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever I can to help,\Nso don't hold back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- See you!\N- See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, to be honest, I'm about 99% sure\Nyour hypothesis is nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But 1% of me says\Nit's not totally impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Looking at it from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like I'm just wrapped up\Nin a game of make-believe crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if it is make-believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part of it may be down\Nto these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a strong sense your thinking\Nis going to lead to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You trusted me enough\Nto tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to believe in you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you for my own sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the flip side to someone\Nsaying "please believe me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could've saved her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what I said when I was crying\Nin front of Mom 18 years ago?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to feel that way again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let anyone be alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can save them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to get a parent's signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come\Nwith me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, wanna go to the hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. There's something we have to do.
